{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gridle is an <strong>incremental idle RPG</strong> where you\u2019ll manage a powerful party to take down waves of enemies! Strategically upgrade, heal, reassign, and level up your party members to ensure maximum progress. After 50 initial levels to conquer, the game transitions into infinite levels where the challenge never stops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439430/extras/Title_IdleGameplay.gif?t=1736883049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your party will automatically fight enemies for you. Allowing you to do other tasks while the gameplay flows. Optimize your party for survival to ensure they progress as much as possible by assigning classes to your party slots, upgrading your classes, unlocking skills, rebirthing for knowledge upgrades and much more.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439430/extras/idle.gif?t=1736883049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rebirth</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gridle features a huge rebirth tree with well over 200<i> knowledge upgrades</i>. These upgrades impact everything from money earnings to individual class perks and will ensure your party can go way beyond any limits and eventually reach the<i> end of the realm</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439430/extras/rebirth.gif?t=1736883049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439430/extras/Title_Roadmap.png?t=1736883049\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets